      "index": "ag",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1942149382,
      "version": 604,
      "versionNonce": 1874970768,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777752936199,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. MCS changes :\n    instruction + knowledge change\n    put mcp server basic contract details in knowledge\n    mentioned fallback to tools if mcp fails\n    put retry in knowledge\n2. mcp server:\n    certain type of entity operation werent supported\n   we had to co dev \n    custom apis remained same\n    decision to invoke tools was still with mcs, it hallucinated\n        WHY? no of tools increased, lot of global tools",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. MCS changes :\n    instruction + knowledge change\n    put mcp server basic contract details in knowledge\n    mentioned fallback to tools if mcp fails\n    put retry in knowledge\n2. mcp server:\n    certain type of entity operation werent supported\n   we had to co dev \n    custom apis remained same\n    decision to invoke tools was still with mcs, it hallucinated\n        WHY? no of tools increased, lot of global tools",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
